## âš¡ Day 8 â€” How Software Gets Built
**Plain English:** Understand how ideas turn into shipped softwareâ€”and where governance fits.

- Learn the **SDLC**: idea â†’ backlog â†’ build â†’ test â†’ review â†’ merge â†’ deploy â†’ monitor
